They bribe their special interests with massive subsidies -solar, wind, teachers unions, you name it. And then they tell you it’s for your own good. They tell you to forget about inflation or the debt your kids will owe. You don’t believe them, so they add more spending to the bill and tell you it’s for you. node.text: Reducing emissions without killing our economy is actually pretty doable with a mix of nuclear and natural gas and carbon capture. But Democrats don’t actually want to reduce emissions, they just want us to use solar and wind. It’s a single focus solution that means higher prices and less reliable energy. They don’t actually think climate change is an imminent threat. If they did, they’d spend the money in this bill on new nuclear plants.

node.text: For about 48 hours the Energy and Commerce Committee is debating sections of the absurd $3.5T spending bill. If there’s one thing to remember about this bill, it is this: their spending is nothing but bribery. They bribe their special interests with massive subsidies -solar, wind, teachers unions, you name it. And then they tell you it’s for your own good. They tell you to forget about inflation or the debt your kids will owe. You don’t believe them, so they add more spending to the bill and tell you it’s for you. They try and bribe YOU into voting for them. And they’re bribing you with your own money and your children’s debt.
